:Initialize an empty dictionary `num_to_index`;
repeat
 :Iterate over `nums` with index `i` and value `num`;
 :Calculate `complement = target - num`;

 if (Is `complement` in `num_to_index`?) then (yes)
 :Return [num_to_index[complement], i];
 stop
 else (no)
 :Add `num` to `num_to_index` with index `i`;
 endif
